cs.DB, cs.OS, cs.DC, cs.PL, cs.SE 

This paper focuses on improving the predictability of performance in database management systems (DBMSs), which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes a profiling framework and analyzes two open-source DBMSs, which involves operating systems (cs.OS) and distributed computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper proposes new algorithms and tuning parameters, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE).
